setWaypointCombatMode 
Game: Armed Assault (1.00) 
Description: The group combat mode is switched when the waypoint becomes active 
. 
Possible mode values are: "NO CHANGE" (No change) "BLUE" (Never fire 
) "GREEN" (Hold fire - defend only) "WHITE" (Hold fire, engage at will 
) "YELLOW" (Fire at will) "RED" (Fire at will, engage at will) 
Syntax:  
 waypoint setWaypointCombatMode mode 
Parameters: 
waypoint: Array - format Waypoint 
mode: String 
Return Value: 
 Nothing